<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Learning about shodows in css</title>
    <style>
      .a1 {
        margin: 10px;
        padding: 30px;
        border: 2px solid purple;
        box-shadow: 5px 5px 15px 5px #ee0a0af7;
      }
      .myline{
       margin: 10px;
        padding: 30px;
        border: 2px solid rgb(4, 128, 0);
        box-shadow: 5px 5px 15px 5px #520aeef7;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px #888888;
        /* we use outline offset to change outline size it is not fixed like border */
         outline: 2px solid blue;
        outline-offset: 100px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="apple a1">
      hey am learning about css shadows and enjoying learning css
    </div>
    <div class="myline">
      <p>
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. In, illo?
        Voluptatibus, deserunt exercitationem minima ullam beatae porro, veniam
        culpa facere quod quibusdam accusantium dolorem? Cum eligendi rerum
        dicta optio? Quidem!
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
